        <div class="pitch">
          <h1>Live Video-Streaming in iOS</h1>
          <p>
            With the cine.io iOS SDK, you can publish live RTMP streams right
            from your iPhone or iPad. The h.264 and AAC encoding happens in a
            hardware-accelerated way, so you don't need to worry about battery
            life. Our backend handles the conversion to HLS for consumption on
            any compatible device. Both Objective-C and Swift are supported.
          </p>
